Entry.JapaneseText: いいかげんに機嫌直せよな、<Mao>！ 夢だろ……!?
Entry.EnglishText: Oh come on, lighten up, <Mao>! Wasn't it just a dream?!

Entry.JapaneseText: だって！ もう少しで、すっごい ごちそう食べられそうだったのにぃ！
Entry.EnglishText: But! Just a little while longer, and I would've been chowing down on some gourmet food!

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>が起こしたりするから！ 食べものの恨みは怖いんだヨ!!
Entry.EnglishText: You just had to go and wake me up! You won't like me when I'm hangry!

Entry.JapaneseText: 腹がへるから、機嫌が悪くなるんだ。 <Tytree>、なんか作ってやってくれ。
Entry.EnglishText: He's in a sour mood because he's hungry. <Tytree>, make him something to eat.

Entry.JapaneseText: まったく……このチビッコは 手間がかかるぜ……
Entry.EnglishText: Geez... This kid sure is a handful...
